<plot>This documentary treats movie fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of Never Cry Wolf, the film version of Farley Mowat's book about his experiences researching the behavior of wolves in the wild. Included are interviews with the cast and crew who talk about the experience of making the film, as well as all of the effort that went into it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?574005</url></doc>
